464
00:28:05,934 --> 00:28:09,552
her throat torn to
pieces by an enraged cat.

465
00:28:15,027 --> 00:28:16,688
Burned to death,

466
00:28:18,405 --> 00:28:20,066
buried alive,

467
00:28:20,991 --> 00:28:22,652
tortured,

