00:28:55,943 --> 00:28:57,649
Full of life,

474
00:28:59,821 --> 00:29:01,436
beautiful and innocent,

475
00:29:02,241 --> 00:29:04,072
like life in the 60s,

476
00:29:06,411 --> 00:29:08,402
like my life at the time.

